title: Episode 7 - Frank discusses the latest developments on Fannie Mae and Freddie Mac with banking analyst Richard Suttmeier
itunes:title: Frank discusses the latest developments on Fannie Mae and Freddie Mac with banking analyst Richard Suttmeier
description:
Frank
and chief market strategist Rich Suttmeier from Valuengine.com debate whether
Fannie and Freddie should even exist. Frank also breaks down retail sales and
illustrates one of his favorite investment techniques for picking winners under
$10
